data.description: This fully furnished, move-in-ready home is perfect for families or investors seeking a chic and well-maintained property. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a 1-car garage, the home features a spacious master bedroom, media room, and entertainment area. The kitchen is equipped with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, while the living room offers a cozy fireplace. The property also includes a complete finished basement, a large deck with a hot tub, and ample yard parking. Situated just 20 minutes from I-85 and 10 minutes from I-20, this home presents an ideal opportunity for those looking to add a fully furnished short-term rental to their investment portfolio. The seller is willing to include all furniture, providing a hassle-free transition for the new owner. Don't miss out on the chance to make this well-designed and versatile home yours.
